{"tid":1425801,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"真心唔明, 唔比影相係咪有用.","createTime":"2019-08-06T21:05:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T07:28:16.000Z","uid":156298,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fbd73ba869123f1a03fe4f962df630cc4ea34ab0","tid":1425801,"uid":156298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T21:05:59.000Z","msg":"唔好屌住...... 你都係屌啦, 屌完聽下.<br />\n<br />\n現場兩類人, 人, 鬼..<br />\n鬼既, 插個差佬用果種鏡頭, 4K, HDR, 乜都錄晒. 要乜有乜, 舉單反果啲, 冇腦既啫. <br />\n就算係GoPro, 都唔見得前線有人會stop 佢, 因為自保好正常. <br />\n而家 Video Cam, Sony CCD 4K 清到嚇死人.<br />\n<br />\n人既, 佢唔會賣你, 就算係話比差佬逗晒啲相出來, 又如何? 現場相大把, 差佬係防線後用100X Zoom 好過你手機影大頭.<br />\n<br />\n重要既係, 一出事, 求相, 求片... 冇呀, 唔比影呀. 結果現場相得差佬同鬼有.. 官司你打條毛呀?<br />\n惟有希望啲唔聽話既街坊有偷拍."},{"pid":"55ba9df6c1cd1020ae15e1b41f6856a93cd577c5","tid":1425801,"uid":29283,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T21:07:10.000Z","msg":"其實我都覺太大反應啦"},{"pid":"2e13a54b0ebf127b4259dc4a46041d23bb127a46","tid":1425801,"uid":82829,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"55ba9df6c1cd1020ae15e1b41f6856a93cd577c5","tid":1425801,"uid":29283,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T21:07:10.000Z","msg":"其實我都覺太大反應啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T21:08:15.000Z","msg":"咁你又不推放回覆？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2c7d9a0001648a66e4c7e5489879729750e63f2","tid":1425801,"uid":29283,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2e13a54b0ebf127b4259dc4a46041d23bb127a46","tid":1425801,"uid":82829,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"55ba9df6c1cd1020ae15e1b41f6856a93cd577c5","tid":1425801,"uid":29283,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T21:07:10.000Z","msg":"其實我都覺太大反應啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T21:08:15.000Z","msg":"咁你又不推放回覆？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T21:10:02.000Z","msg":"唔俾？"},{"pid":"431c58a12436e95a33a9386452961905287fdba3","ti